19:17.449 --> 19:18.597
What's this?

19:18.599 --> 19:20.722
Your birth certificate.

19:20.724 --> 19:24.404
Your real dad's name is...

19:24.406 --> 19:27.588
C. Wilder.

19:27.590 --> 19:29.102
How'd you find this?

19:29.104 --> 19:31.174
Eh, my family
has a PI on retainer.

19:31.176 --> 19:33.031
It's handy.

19:33.033 --> 19:34.229
