19:34.231 --> 19:35.498
Want to go find him?

19:41.843 --> 19:43.306
- Peterson?
- Mm-hmm.

19:43.308 --> 19:45.675
- Williams?
- Mm.

19:45.677 --> 19:47.727
- Avilez.
- Yup.

19:47.729 --> 19:49.439
- Harvey.
- Here.

19:49.441 --> 19:51.208
- Jones.
- Mm-hmm.

19:51.210 --> 19:53.481
Being a lifeguard is such
a huge responsibility.

19:53.483 --> 19:54.211
Worthy?

19:54.213 --> 19:56.301
Maybe later, we should
practice mouth-to-mouth.

19:56.303 --> 19:58.084
Ashcroft?

19:58.086 --> 20:00.768
- Ashcroft?
- Ashcroft?

